Cmd=-analyzeduration 1500k -threads {threads} {offset} {realtime} -i "{infile}" -threads {threads} -f mpegts -pat_period 0.2 -vcodec libx264 -bufsize 1400k -maxrate 650k -crf 24 -g 50 {framerate} -map 0:0 -map 0:1 -vf "yadif=0:-1:1, scale={scalex}:{scaley}" -preset {vpreset} -tune film -vprofile baseline -level 30 -acodec libmp3lame -ab 48k -ar 44100 -ac 1 -async 1 -y "{outfile}"
maxWidth=512
maxHeight=360
MimeType=video/mpeg
Ext=.ts

[TS Lowest 400 kbit]
Cmd=-analyzeduration 1500k -threads {threads} {offset} {realtime} -i "{infile}" -threads {threads} -f mpegts -pat_period 0.2 -vcodec libx264 -bufsize 600k -maxrate 300k -crf 25 -g 50 {framerate} -map 0:0 -map 0:1 -vf "yadif=0:-1:1, scale={scalex}:{scaley}" -preset {vpreset} -tune film -vprofile baseline -level 30 -acodec libmp3lame -ab 32k -ar 32000 -ac 1 -async 1 -y "{outfile}"
maxWidth=480
maxHeight=270
MimeType=video/mpeg

MimeType=audio/mpeg
